{"tid":1222381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解身邊嘅人仲係未覺醒","createTime":"2019-06-14T12:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T12:53:55.000Z","uid":200021,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e19742b96d0be9b522108cf6e1dd3c964577cb10","tid":1222381,"uid":200021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:05:14.000Z","msg":"今朝係咁用啊媽部手機send啲長輩圖俾佢嘅親中朋友睇<br />\n個個睇完就求其覆emoji就算<br />\n有個仲話:唔明搞亂香港 對下一代有咩好處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（不過繼續send俾其他人 我信總會拉到人支持反送中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n之後我細佬考完試返屋企<br />\n我問佢啲同學知唔知香港發生跟咩事<br />\n佢竟然話佢啲同學好支持香港政府<br />\n仲話要畢咗業之後考警犬 做速龍打示威者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽完真係好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲義士咁努力為香港爭取<br />\n但係香港仲有咁多港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過好彩我全屋人都支持我發夢去幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已拉大隊去616遊行<br />\n各位到時見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">千萬不要鬆懈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n撤回惡法 釋放被捕人士先係我地目標！</span>"},{"pid":"9e5829f10c3cb8ef8e63b6b3c0139ed9872a762d","tid":1222381,"uid":179409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:34:35.000Z","msg":"每個社會都一關<br />\n關心社會嘅人永遠係佔少數<br />\nWFC先係主流<br />\n香港佔到七分之一<br />\n已經算係好多"},{"pid":"6da94e6be73ddfe60aede2b1d931b8ed27803a48","tid":1222381,"uid":179409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e5829f10c3cb8ef8e63b6b3c0139ed9872a762d","tid":1222381,"uid":179409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:34:35.000Z","msg":"每個社會都一關<br />\n關心社會嘅人永遠係佔少數<br />\nWFC先係主流<br />\n香港佔到七分之一<br />\n已經算係好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:35:04.000Z","msg":"每個社會都一<span style=\"color: red;\">樣</span>"},{"pid":"8784ad2fe952ab89e01791574b3eb1518d33afb4","tid":1222381,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:37:05.000Z","msg":"當年辛亥革命都係一樣啦<br />\n<br />\n當時清帝國有四億人<br />\n但參與革命 都係得幾千人, 幾萬人左右<br />\n<br />\n不過已經足夠成為導水線推翻清帝國"},{"pid":"dcb9a908be908b0479d75654eab6405a9bd285e1","tid":1222381,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:53:55.000Z","msg":"中國傳統懦家思想<br />\n<br />\n註：懦，懦夫也"}]}